@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #83107 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
erroneous code and the panic message tells what is wrong, P-low, or P-medium if someone thinks this should be fixed soonish

We usually assign P-medium to ICEs of this kind I think (even on non working code) so I'll stick to that.
(but I'm ok with lowering it either)
